parameters:
\N<Taro>W-What is this place... Amazing, it's got a full set of
living supplies!

\N<Luna>Everything's covered in dust, but the furniture is all here,
and the water... it's clean enough to drink♪
\N<Taro>Why is there such a secluded hideaway by the seaside...

\N<Luna>It must have been made by adventurers like us in the past as
a base... It seems no one lives here now, so let's take
advantage of it♪

\N<Taro>...Yeah, this place looks good enough to rest in... It'll
protect us from the rain and wind, and we might just be able
to live here.

\N<Taro>For now, we should be grateful just to have found a place to
sleep.

\N<Luna>Exactly, it's settled then♪ At least for now, our worries
about living arrangements are cleared up.

\N<Taro>Sorry for being so disorganized and negative... Let's cheer
up and work hard on paying off our debt from now on!

And so, Luna and the others found a base, marking the
beginning of their earnest efforts to repay their debts.
